  "title": "Visibility and Attention Debt",
  "concept": "A community's collective attention for recognition accumulates slowly through repeated exposure — when loss arrives, acknowledgment depends on whether sufficient attention has already been deposited, not on the magnitude of the loss itself.",
  "interactiveId": "17f9d7c2-808e-48b3-8837-2c1a119aa24c",
  "sourcePieceId": "2f1d9adf-66ac-42ac-80c6-230a72bb8fdc",
  "publishedAt": 1777297161039,
  "voiceScore": 88,
  "qualityFlag": "low",
  "content": {
    "type": "html",
    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n<title>Visibility and Attention Debt</title>\n<style>\n  :root {\n    --bg: #faf7f1;\n    --fg: #1a1a1a;\n    --muted: #6b6b6b;\n    --line: #e5e0d6;\n    --deposit: #1a6b62;\n    --loss: #c9a227;\n    --insufficient: #d4a574;\n  }\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n  body {\n    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif;\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 20px;\n    color: var(--fg);\n    background: var(--bg);\n    line-height: 1.5;\n  }\n  h2 {\n    font-size: 1.05rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin: 0 0 4px;\n  }\n  p.subhead {\n    margin: 0 0 20px;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .timeline-container {\n    margin: 24px 0;\n    max-width: 600px;\n  }\n  .timeline {\n    position: relative;\n    height: 160px;\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n  .timeline-track {\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: 0;\n    left: 0;\n    right: 0;\n    height: 60px;\n    background: var(--line);\n  }\n  .attention-bar {\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: 0;\n    left: 0;\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 0;\n    background: var(--deposit);\n    transition: height 300ms ease-out;\n  }\n  .loss-marker {\n    position: absolute;\n    right: 16px;\n    bottom: 60px;\n    width: 8px;\n    height: 80px;\n    background: var(--loss);\n    border-radius: 4px 4px 0 0;\n    opacity: 0;\n    transition: opacity 200ms ease-in;\n  }\n  .loss-marker.visible {\n    opacity: 1;\n  }\n  .threshold-line {\n    position: absolute;\n    left: 0;\n    right: 0;\n    height: 2px;\n    background: rgba(201, 162, 39, 0.4);\n    pointer-events: none;\n    transition: bottom 300ms ease-out;\n  }\n  .threshold-label {\n    position: absolute;\n    right: 28px;\n    font-size: 0.7rem;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-weight: 600;\n    transition: bottom 300ms ease-out;\n  }\n  .controls {\n    margin: 20px 0;\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 16px;\n    align-items: center;\n  }\n  button {\n    padding: 10px 18px;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    border: 2px solid var(--deposit);\n    background: #fff;\n    color: var(--deposit);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: all 120ms ease-out;\n  }\n  button:hover {\n    background: var(--deposit);\n    color: #fff;\n  }\n  button:disabled {\n    opacity: 0.4;\n    cursor: not-allowed;\n  }\n  button.loss-btn {\n    border-color: var(--loss);\n    color: var(--loss);\n  }\n  button.loss-btn:hover {\n    background: var(--loss);\n    color: #fff;\n  }\n  button.reset-btn {\n    border-color: var(--muted);\n    color: var(--muted);\n  }\n  button.reset-btn:hover {\n    background: var(--muted);\n    color: #fff;\n  }\n  .reading {\n    margin: 18px 0 6px;\n    padding: 10px 14px;\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .reading strong {\n    font-weight: 600;\n  }\n  p.caption {\n    margin: 14px 0 0;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.875rem;\n  }\n  .tick-label {\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: -22px;\n    font-size: 0.7rem;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    transform: translateX(-50%);\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 480px) {\n    .controls {\n      flex-direction: column;\n      align-items: stretch;\n    }\n    button {\n      width: 100%;\n    }\n    .timeline {\n      height: 140px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<h2>Build attention through repeated exposure, then trigger loss</h2>\n<p class=\"subhead\">Each exposure deposits attention. Loss requires accumulated attention to generate recognition.</p>\n\n<div class=\"timeline-container\">\n  <div class=\"timeline\" id=\"timeline\">\n    <div class=\"attention-bar\" id=\"attention-bar\"></div>\n    <div class=\"threshold-line\" id=\"threshold-line\"></div>\n    <div class=\"threshold-label\" id=\"threshold-label\">Recognition threshold</div>\n    <div class=\"loss-marker\" id=\"loss-marker\"></div>\n    <div class=\"tick-label\" style=\"left: 0;\">Start</div>\n    <div class=\"tick-label\" style=\"left: 100%; transform: translateX(-100%);\">Now</div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"controls\">\n  <button id=\"expose-btn\" class=\"expose-btn\">Add exposure (+15 units)</button>\n  <button id=\"loss-btn\" class=\"loss-btn\" disabled>Trigger loss event</button>\n  <button id=\"reset-btn\" class=\"reset-btn\">Reset</button>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"reading\">\n  Accumulated attention: <strong id=\"accumulated\">0</strong> units.<br>\n  Recognition threshold: <strong id=\"threshold-val\">60</strong> units.<br>\n  Status: <strong id=\"status\">No loss triggered</strong>.\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"caption\" id=\"caption\">Attention accumulates through repeated exposure. The community builds a reserve slowly. When loss arrives, recognition depends on whether the reserve meets the threshold.</p>\n\n<script>\n  (function () {\n    var accumulated = 0;\n    var threshold = 60;\n    var lossTriggered = false;\n    var maxHeight = 60;\n    \n    var attentionBar = document.getElementById('attention-bar');\n    var lossMarker = document.getElementById('loss-marker');\n    var thresholdLine = document.getElementById('threshold-line');\n    var thresholdLabel = document.getElementById('threshold-label');\n    var exposeBtn = document.getElementById('expose-btn');\n    var lossBtn = document.getElementById('loss-btn');\n    var resetBtn = document.getElementById('reset-btn');\n    var accumulatedText = document.getElementById('accumulated');\n    var thresholdValText = document.getElementById('threshold-val');\n    var statusText = document.getElementById('status');\n    var caption = document.getElementById('caption');\n\n    function updateDisplay() {\n      var heightPercent = Math.min((accumulated / 100) * 100, 100);\n      attentionBar.style.height = heightPercent + '%';\n      \n      var thresholdPercent = (threshold / 100) * 100;\n      thresholdLine.style.bottom = thresholdPercent + '%';\n      thresholdLabel.style.bottom = 'calc(' + thresholdPercent + '% + 4px)';\n      \n      accumulatedText.textContent = accumulated;\n      thresholdValText.textContent = threshold;\n      \n      if (accumulated >= 15 && !lossTriggered) {\n        lossBtn.disabled = false;\n      }\n      \n      if (!lossTriggered) {\n        if (accumulated === 0) {\n          statusText.textContent = 'No loss triggered';\n          caption.textContent = 'Attention accumulates through repeated exposure. The community builds a reserve slowly. When loss arrives, recognition depends on whether the reserve meets the threshold.';\n        } else if (accumulated < threshold) {\n          statusText.textContent = 'Building reserve (' + Math.round((accumulated/threshold)*100) + '% of threshold)';\n          caption.textContent = 'Each exposure deposits attention. The reserve grows incrementally. Loss has not yet arrived.';\n        } else {\n          statusText.textContent = 'Reserve exceeds threshold';\n          caption.textContent = 'The accumulated reserve now exceeds the recognition threshold. If loss arrives, collective acknowledgment happens automatically.';\n        }\n      }\n    }\n\n    exposeBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {\n      if (lossTriggered) return;\n      accumulated += 15;\n      if (accumulated > 100) accumulated = 100;\n      updateDisplay();\n      if (window.parent) {\n        window.parent.postMessage({type: 'interactive_engagement', event: 'manipulated'}, '*');\n      }\n    });\n\n    lossBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {\n      if (lossTriggered) return;\n      lossTriggered = true;\n      lossMarker.classList.add('visible');\n      lossBtn.disabled = true;\n      exposeBtn.disabled = true;\n      \n      if (accumulated >= threshold) {\n        statusText.textContent = 'Recognition granted';\n        caption.textContent = 'The accumulated reserve (' + accumulated + ' units) meets the threshold (' + threshold + ' units). Collective recognition happens because attention was deposited before loss arrived, not because the loss itself was larger.';\n      } else {\n        var deficit = threshold - accumulated;\n        statusText.textContent = 'Recognition denied';\n        caption.textContent = 'The accumulated reserve (' + accumulated + ' units) falls short of the threshold (' + threshold + ' units) by ' + deficit + ' units. Recognition does not happen — not because the loss is small, but because insufficient attention was deposited beforehand.';\n      }\n      \n      if (window.parent) {\n        window.parent.postMessage({type: 'interactive_engagement', event: 'manipulated'}, '*');\n      }\n    });\n\n    resetBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {\n      accumulated = 0;\n      lossTriggered = false;\n      lossMarker.classList.remove('visible');\n      lossBtn.disabled = true;\n      exposeBtn.disabled = false;\n      updateDisplay();\n      if (window.parent) {\n        window.parent.postMessage({type: 'interactive_engagement', event: 'manipulated'}, '*');\n      }\n    });\n\n    updateDisplay();\n  })();\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>"
  }
}
